[{"title":"TailwindCSS Editor","content":"<h1>TailwindCSS Code Editor</h1><div class=\"page-nav-buttons\"><button class=\"btn-secondary prev-btn\" disabled>❮ Home</button><button class=\"btn-primary next-btn\">Next ❯</button></div><div class=\"content-section\"><h3>Interactive TailwindCSS Playground</h3><p class=\"text-block\">Practice TailwindCSS directly in your browser! This editor provides full Tailwind v3+ utility classes, responsive breakpoints, hover/focus states, dark mode, and component building.</p><br><button class=\"btn-try-it\" style=\"margin: 0 0 15px 0; font-size: 18px; padding: 15px 30px;\" onclick=\"window.open('editor/tailwindcss-editor.html', '_blank')\">🚀 Open Tailwind Editor</button></div><div class=\"content-section\"><h3>What You Can Practice</h3><ul class=\"feature-list\"><li><strong>Utility Classes</strong> - Spacing, colors, typography, layout</li><li><strong>Responsive Design</strong> - sm:, md:, lg: breakpoints</li><li><strong>State Variants</strong> - hover:, focus:, active:</li><li><strong>Components</strong> - Buttons, cards, navbars, forms</li><li><strong>Dark Mode</strong> - dark: prefix</li><li><strong>Custom Config</strong> - Extend theme</li></ul></div><div class=\"content-section\"><h3>Pro Tips</h3><ul class=\"feature-list\"><li><strong>Ctrl + Enter</strong> to run/preview code</li><li>IntelliSense for all Tailwind classes</li><li>Live preview with responsive simulation</li></ul></div><div class=\"page-nav-buttons bottom-nav\"><button class=\"btn-secondary prev-btn\" disabled>❮ Home</button><button class=\"btn-primary next-btn\">Next ❯</button></div>"},{"title":"TailwindCSS Introduction","content":"<h1>TailwindCSS Introduction</h1><div class=\"page-nav-buttons\"><button class=\"btn-secondary prev-btn\">❮ Previous</button><button class=\"btn-primary next-btn\">Next ❯</button></div><div class=\"content-section\"><h3>Utility-First CSS Framework</h3><p class=\"text-block\">Tailwind CSS is a utility-first CSS framework for rapidly building custom designs. Instead of opinionated components, Tailwind provides low-level utility classes you compose to create any design directly in HTML.</p></div><div class=\"content-section\"><h3>Why Tailwind?</h3><ul class=\"feature-list\"><li><strong>Fast Development:</strong> No context-switching between files</li><li><strong>Consistent Design:</strong> Standardized spacing/color system</li><li><strong>Small Bundle:</strong> Tree-shaking removes unused CSS</li><li><strong>Fully Customizable:</strong> Extend/extend theme via JS config</li></ul><div class=\"syntax-wrapper\"><div class=\"syntax-header\">Basic Example</div><div class=\"code-editor\"><pre><div class=\"bg-blue-500 text-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-lg\">\n  Hello Tailwind!\n</div></pre></div><br><button class=\"btn-try-it\" style=\"margin: 0 0 15px 15px;\">Try it Yourself »</button></div></div><div class=\"page-nav-buttons bottom-nav\"><button class=\"btn-secondary prev-btn\">❮ Previous</button><button class=\"btn-primary next-btn\">Next ❯</button></div>"},{"title":"Installation & Setup","content":"<h1>TailwindCSS Installation</h1><div class=\"page-nav-buttons\"><button class=\"btn-secondary prev-btn\">❮ Previous</button><button class=\"btn-primary next-btn\">Next ❯</button></div><div class=\"content-section\"><h3>Quick Install (CDN for prototyping)</h3><div class=\"syntax-wrapper\"><div class=\"syntax-header\">HTML CDN</div><div class=\"code-editor\"><pre><script src=\"https://cdn.tailwindcss.com\"></script></pre></div></div><div class=\"content-section\"><h3>Production Install (PostCSS)</h3><div class=\"syntax-wrapper\"><div class=\"syntax-header\">Terminal Commands</div><div class=\"code-editor\"><pre>npm install -D tailwindcss postcss autoprefixer\nnpx tailwindcss init -p</pre></div></div><div class=\"syntax-wrapper\"><div class=\"syntax-header\">tailwind.config.js</div><div class=\"code-editor\"><pre>module.exports = {\n  content: ['./src/**/*.{html,js}'],\n  theme: { extend: {} },\n  plugins: [],\n}</pre></div></div><div class=\"syntax-wrapper\"><div class=\"syntax-header\">input.css</div><div class=\"code-editor\"><pre>@tailwind base;\n@tailwind components;\n@tailwind utilities;</pre></div></div><br><button class=\"btn-try-it\" style=\"margin: 0 0 15px 15px;\">Try it Yourself »</button></div></div><div class=\"page-nav-buttons bottom-nav\"><button class=\"btn-secondary prev-btn\">❮ Previous</button><button class=\"btn-primary next-btn\">Next ❯</button></div>"},{"title":"Core Concepts - Utilities","content":"<h1>Core Utilities</h1><div class=\"page-nav-buttons\"><button class=\"btn-secondary prev-btn\">❮ Previous</button><button class=\"btn-primary next-btn\">Next ❯</button></div><div class=\"content-section\"><h3>Spacing Scale</h3><p class=\"text-block\">Tailwind uses a consistent 0.25rem (4px) spacing scale: p-1 (0.25rem), p-2 (0.5rem), up to p-96 (24rem).</p><div class=\"syntax-wrapper\"><div class=\"syntax-header\">Spacing Examples</div><div class=\"code-editor\"><pre><div class=\"p-4 m-2 bg-gray-200 rounded\">\n  Padding (p-) &amp; Margin (m-)\n</div>\n<div class=\"p-8 mx-4 bg-blue-100\">\n  Larger padding/margin\n</div></pre></div><br><button class=\"btn-try-it\" style=\"margin: 0 0 15px 15px;\">Try it Yourself »</button></div></div><div class=\"content-section\"><h3>Colors</h3><p class=\"text-block\">50 shades per color (50-950), opacity modifiers (bg-blue-500/50).</p></div><div class=\"page-nav-buttons bottom-nav\"><button class=\"btn-secondary prev-btn\">❮ Previous</button><button class=\"btn-primary next-btn\">Next ❯</button></div>"},{"title":"Typography Utilities","content":"<h1>Typography</h1><div class=\"page-nav-buttons\"><button class=\"btn-secondary prev-btn\">❮ Previous</button><button class=\"btn-primary next-btn\">Next ❯</button></div><div class=\"content-section\"><h3>Font Size & Weight</h3><div class=\"syntax-wrapper\"><div class=\"syntax-header\">Typography Classes</div><div class=\"code-editor\"><pre><h1 class=\"text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4\">\n  Heading 1\n</h1>\n<p class=\"text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\">\n  Body text with comfortable line-height\n</p>\n<p class=\"text-sm font-medium text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wide\">\n  Small label text\n</p></pre></div><br><button class=\"btn-try-it\" style=\"margin: 0 0 15px 15px;\">Try it Yourself »</button></div></div><div class=\"content-section\"><h3>Text Alignment & Transform</h3><p class=\"text-block\">text-left/right/center/justify, uppercase/lowercase/capitalize.</p></div><div class=\"page-nav-buttons bottom-nav\"><button class=\"btn-secondary prev-btn\">❮ Previous</button><button class=\"btn-primary next-btn\">Next ❯</button></div>"},{"title":"Layout - Flexbox","content":"<h1>Flexbox Utilities</h1><div class=\"page-nav-buttons\"><button class=\"btn-secondary prev-btn\">❮ Previous</button><button class=\"btn-primary next-btn\">Next ❯</button></div><div class=\"content-section\"><h3>Flex Container</h3><div class=\"syntax-wrapper\"><div class=\"syntax-header\">Flex Examples</div><div class=\"code-editor\"><pre><div class=\"flex justify-between items-center p-6 bg-white shadow\">\n  <div class=\"flex items-center space-x-4\">\n    <img src=\"logo.png\" class=\"h-8\">\n    <span>Dashboard</span>\n  </div>\n  <button class=\"px-4 py-2 bg-blue-500 text-white rounded\">\n    New\n  </button>\n</div></pre></div><br><button class=\"btn-try-it\" style=\"margin: 0 0 15px 15px;\">Try it Yourself »</button></div></div><div class=\"content-section\"><h3>Key Classes</h3><ul class=\"feature-list\"><li>flex / flex-col / flex-wrap</li><li>justify-start/end/center/between/around/evenly</li><li>items-start/end/center/baseline/stretch</li><li>space-x-4 / space-y-2 (gaps)</li></ul></div><div class=\"page-nav-buttons bottom-nav\"><button class=\"btn-secondary prev-btn\">❮ Previous</button><button class=\"btn-primary next-btn\">Next ❯</button></div>"},{"title":"Layout - Grid","content":"<h1>CSS Grid Utilities</h1><div class=\"page-nav-buttons\"><button class=\"btn-secondary prev-btn\">❮ Previous</button><button class=\"btn-primary next-btn\">Next ❯</button></div><div class=\"content-section\"><h3>Grid Layout</h3><div class=\"syntax-wrapper\"><div class=\"syntax-header\">Grid Examples</div><div class=\"code-editor\"><pre><div class=\"grid grid-cols-3 gap-6 p-8 bg-gray-50\">\n  <div class=\"col-span-2 row-span-2 bg-blue-500 text-white p-6 rounded-lg\">\n    Main Content\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"bg-green-500 text-white p-6 rounded-lg\">Sidebar</div>\n  <div class=\"bg-yellow-500 text-white p-6 rounded-lg\">Card 1</div>\n</div></pre></div><br><button class=\"btn-try-it\" style=\"margin: 0 0 15px 15px;\">Try it Yourself »</button></div></div><div class=\"content-section\"><h3>Key Classes</h3><ul class=\"feature-list\"><li>grid / grid-cols-{n}</li><li>gap-4 / col-span-2 / row-span-1</li><li>place-items-center / justify-items-center</li></ul></div><div class=\"page-nav-buttons bottom-nav\"><button class=\"btn-secondary prev-btn\">❮ Previous</button><button class=\"btn-primary next-btn\">Next ❯</button></div>"},{"title":"Responsive Design","content":"<h1>Responsive Utilities</h1><div class=\"page-nav-buttons\"><button class=\"btn-secondary prev-btn\">❮ Previous</button><button class=\"btn-primary next-btn\">Next ❯</button></div><div class=\"content-section\"><h3>Mobile-First Breakpoints</h3><p class=\"text-block\">Prefixes: default (mobile), sm: (640px+), md: (768px+), lg: (1024px+), xl: (1280px+), 2xl: (1536px+).</p><div class=\"syntax-wrapper\"><div class=\"syntax-header\">Responsive Navbar</div><div class=\"code-editor\"><pre><nav class=\"flex flex-col lg:flex-row lg:space-x-8 p-4 lg:p-8\">\n  <div class=\"flex flex-col lg:flex-row lg:space-x-8 mb-4 lg:mb-0\">\n    <a href=\"#\" class=\"text-xl font-bold mb-2 lg:mb-0\">Logo</a>\n    <a href=\"#\" class=\"py-2\">Home</a>\n  </div>\n</nav></pre></div><br><button class=\"btn-try-it\" style=\"margin: 0 0 15px 15px;\">Try it Yourself »</button></div></div><div class=\"page-nav-buttons bottom-nav\"><button class=\"btn-secondary prev-btn\">❮ Previous</button><button class=\"btn-primary next-btn\">Next ❯</button></div>"},{"title":"Interactive States","content":"<h1>Hover, Focus & Active</h1><div class=\"page-nav-buttons\"><button class=\"btn-secondary prev-btn\">❮ Previous</button><button class=\"btn-primary next-btn\">Next ❯</button></div><div class=\"content-section\"><h3>State Variants</h3><div class=\"syntax-wrapper\"><div class=\"syntax-header\">Interactive Button</div><div class=\"code-editor\"><pre><button class=\"px-6 py-3 bg-blue-500 hover:bg-blue-600 active:bg-blue-700 \n  focus:ring-4 focus:ring-blue-300 focus:outline-none rounded-lg \n  transition-all duration-200 transform hover:scale-105\">\n  Click Me\n</button></pre></div><br><button class=\"btn-try-it\" style=\"margin: 0 0 15px 15px;\">Try it Yourself »</button></div></div><div class=\"content-section\"><h3>Common Variants</h3><ul class=\"feature-list\"><li>hover:bg-blue-600</li><li>focus:ring-4 focus:ring-blue-300</li><li>active:scale-95</li><li>group-hover:scale-110</li></ul></div><div class=\"page-nav-buttons bottom-nav\"><button class=\"btn-secondary prev-btn\">❮ Previous</button><button class=\"btn-primary next-btn\">Next ❯</button></div>"},{"title":"Building Components","content":"<h1>Common Components</h1><div class=\"page-nav-buttons\"><button class=\"btn-secondary prev-btn\">❮ Previous</button><button class=\"btn-primary next-btn\">Next ❯</button></div><div class=\"content-section\"><h3>Card Component</h3><div class=\"syntax-wrapper\"><div class=\"syntax-header\">Reusable Card</div><div class=\"code-editor\"><pre><div class=\"max-w-sm bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-xl shadow-md \n  overflow-hidden hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-300\">\n  <img class=\"w-full h-48 object-cover\" src=\"/image.jpg\">\n  <div class=\"p-6\">\n    <h3 class=\"text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2\">\n      Card Title\n    </h3>\n    <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-4\">Description...</p>\n    <button class=\"w-full bg-blue-500 hover:bg-blue-600 text-white \n      py-2 px-4 rounded-lg transition-colors\">\n      Learn More\n    </button>\n  </div>\n</div></pre></div><br><button class=\"btn-try-it\" style=\"margin: 0 0 15px 15px;\">Try it Yourself »</button></div></div><div class=\"page-nav-buttons bottom-nav\"><button class=\"btn-secondary prev-btn\">❮ Previous</button><button class=\"btn-primary next-btn\">Next ❯</button></div>"},{"title":"Dark Mode","content":"<h1>Dark Mode Support</h1><div class=\"page-nav-buttons\"><button class=\"btn-secondary prev-btn\">❮ Previous</button><button class=\"btn-primary next-btn\">Next ❯</button></div><div class=\"content-section\"><h3>dark: Variant</h3><div class=\"syntax-wrapper\"><div class=\"syntax-header\">Dark Mode Card</div><div class=\"code-editor\"><pre><html class=\"dark\">\n<div class=\"bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 border border-gray-200 \n  dark:border-gray-700 text-gray-900 dark:text-white \n  p-6 rounded-xl hover:shadow-lg transition-all\">\n  Dark mode ready!\n</div></pre></div><br><button class=\"btn-try-it\" style=\"margin: 0 0 15px 15px;\">Try it Yourself »</button></div></div><div class=\"content-section\"><h3>Config Setup</h3><div class=\"syntax-wrapper\"><div class=\"syntax-header\">tailwind.config.js</div><div class=\"code-editor\"><pre>module.exports = {\n  darkMode: 'class',\n  // or 'media' for OS preference\n}</pre></div></div></div><div class=\"page-nav-buttons bottom-nav\"><button class=\"btn-secondary prev-btn\">❮ Previous</button><button class=\"btn-primary next-btn\">Next ❯</button></div>"},{"title":"Forms & Inputs","content":"<h1>Form Components</h1><div class=\"page-nav-buttons\"><button class=\"btn-secondary prev-btn\">❮ Previous</button><button class=\"btn-primary next-btn\">Next ❯</button></div><div class=\"content-section\"><h3>Styled Forms</h3><div class=\"syntax-wrapper\"><div class=\"syntax-header\">Form Example</div><div class=\"code-editor\"><pre><form class=\"space-y-4 max-w-md mx-auto p-8 bg-white shadow-lg rounded-xl\">\n  <div>\n    <label class=\"block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-2\">\n      Email\n    </label>\n    <input type=\"email\" class=\"w-full px-3 py-2 border border-gray-300 \n      rounded-lg focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 focus:border-blue-500\" \n      placeholder=\"john@example.com\">\n  </div>\n  <button type=\"submit\" class=\"w-full bg-green-500 hover:bg-green-600 \n    text-white py-2 px-4 rounded-lg font-medium transition-colors\">\n    Submit\n  </button>\n</form></pre></div><br><button class=\"btn-try-it\" style=\"margin: 0 0 15px 15px;\">Try it Yourself »</button></div></div><div class=\"page-nav-buttons bottom-nav\"><button class=\"btn-secondary prev-btn\">❮ Previous</button><button class=\"btn-primary next-btn\">Next ❯</button></div>"},{"title":"Configuration","content":"<h1>Customizing Tailwind</h1><div class=\"page-nav-buttons\"><button class=\"btn-secondary prev-btn\">❮ Previous</button><button class=\"btn-primary next-btn\">Next ❯</button></div><div class=\"content-section\"><h3>Extend Theme</h3><div class=\"syntax-wrapper\"><div class=\"syntax-header\">tailwind.config.js</div><div class=\"code-editor\"><pre>module.exports = {\n  theme: {\n    extend: {\n      colors: {\n        brand: {\n          500: '#1E40AF',\n        }\n      },\n      fontFamily: {\n        sans: ['Inter', 'sans-serif'],\n      },\n      spacing: {\n        '128': '32rem',\n      }\n    }\n  }\n}</pre></div><br><button class=\"btn-try-it\" style=\"margin: 0 0 15px 15px;\">Try it Yourself »</button></div></div><div class=\"content-section\"><h3>Usage</h3><p class=\"text-block\">bg-brand-500, font-sans, p-128</p></div><div class=\"page-nav-buttons bottom-nav\"><button class=\"btn-secondary prev-btn\">❮ Previous</button><button class=\"btn-primary next-btn\">Next ❯</button></div>"},{"title":"JIT Mode","content":"<h1>Just-In-Time (JIT) Mode</h1><div class=\"page-nav-buttons\"><button class=\"btn-secondary prev-btn\">❮ Previous</button><button class=\"btn-primary next-btn\">Next ❯</button></div><div class=\"content-section\"><h3>Generate CSS On-Demand</h3><p class=\"text-block\">Tailwind's JIT engine generates utility classes dynamically as you use them, making builds 100x faster and supporting arbitrary values.</p><div class=\"syntax-wrapper\"><div class=\"syntax-header\">Arbitrary Values</div><div class=\"code-editor\"><pre><div class=\"bg-[#123456] text-[20px] p-[calc(1rem+2vw)] \n  before:content-['Custom!'] before:text-red-500\">\n  JIT Magic!\n</div></pre></div><br><button class=\"btn-try-it\" style=\"margin: 0 0 15px 15px;\">Try it Yourself »</button></div></div><div class=\"content-section\"><h3>Enable JIT</h3><div class=\"syntax-wrapper\"><div class=\"syntax-header\">tailwind.config.js</div><div class=\"code-editor\"><pre>module.exports = {\n  mode: 'jit',\n  // Enabled by default in v3+\n}</pre></div></div></div><div class=\"page-nav-buttons bottom-nav\"><button class=\"btn-secondary prev-btn\">❮ Previous</button><button class=\"btn-primary next-btn\">Next ❯</button></div>"},{"title":"Plugins & Headless UI","content":"<h1>Plugins Ecosystem</h1><div class=\"page-nav-buttons\"><button class=\"btn-secondary prev-btn\">❮ Previous</button><button class=\"btn-primary next-btn\">Next ❯</button></div><div class=\"content-section\"><h3>Official Plugins</h3><div class=\"syntax-wrapper\"><div class=\"syntax-header\">Install Typography Plugin</div><div class=\"code-editor\"><pre>npm install @tailwindcss/typography\n\n// tailwind.config.js\nplugins: [\n  require('@tailwindcss/typography'),\n]</pre></div></div><div class=\"content-section\"><h3>Headless UI</h3><p class=\"text-block\">Unstyled, accessible components (Dialog, Menu, Listbox) that work with Tailwind.</p><div class=\"syntax-wrapper\"><div class=\"syntax-header\">@headlessui/vue</div><div class=\"code-editor\"><pre>npm install @headlessui/vue\n\n<Menu>\n  <MenuButton class=\"px-4 py-2 bg-blue-500 rounded\">\n    Options\n  </MenuButton>\n</Menu></pre></div><br><button class=\"btn-try-it\" style=\"margin: 0 0 15px 15px;\">Try it Yourself »</button></div></div></div><div class=\"page-nav-buttons bottom-nav\"><button class=\"btn-secondary prev-btn\">❮ Previous</button><button class=\"btn-primary next-btn\">Next ❯</button></div>"},{"title":"Best Practices","content":"<h1>Tailwind Best Practices</h1><div class=\"page-nav-buttons\"><button class=\"btn-secondary prev-btn\">❮ Previous</button><button class=\"btn-primary next-btn\">Next ❯</button></div><div class=\"content-section\"><h3>Component Extraction</h3><p class=\"text-block\">Extract repeated utility combinations into custom components.</p><div class=\"syntax-wrapper\"><div class=\"syntax-header\">@apply Directive</div><div class=\"code-editor\"><pre>/* styles.css */\n.btn {\n  @apply px-4 py-2 bg-blue-500 text-white rounded-lg \n         hover:bg-blue-600 active:scale-95 transition-all;\n}\n\n<!-- HTML -->\n<button class=\"btn font-medium\">Click</button></pre></div><br><button class=\"btn-try-it\" style=\"margin: 0 0 15px 15px;\">Try it Yourself »</button></div></div><div class=\"content-section\"><h3>Purge & Optimization</h3><ul class=\"feature-list\"><li>content: ['./src/**/*.{html,js,ts,jsx,tsx}']</li><li>Purge unused CSS automatically</li><li>Use Tailwind Merge for class conflicts</li></ul></div><div class=\"page-nav-buttons bottom-nav\"><button class=\"btn-secondary prev-btn\">❮ Previous</button><button class=\"btn-primary next-btn\">Next ❯</button></div>"},{"title":"TailwindCSS Summary","content":"<h1>TailwindCSS Complete Course Summary 🎨</h1><div class=\"page-nav-buttons\"><button class=\"btn-secondary prev-btn\">❮ Previous</button><button class=\"btn-primary next-btn\" disabled>Next ❯</button></div><div class=\"content-section\"><h3>You Did It! 🎉</h3><p class=\"text-block\">Mastered TailwindCSS! You're now equipped to build beautiful, responsive UIs at lightning speed.</p><ul class=\"feature-list\"><li><strong>Utilities:</strong> Spacing, colors, typography, layout</li><li><strong>Responsive:</strong> Mobile-first breakpoints</li><li><strong>Interactive:</strong> Hover, focus, transitions</li><li><strong>Customization:</strong> Config, plugins, JIT mode</li><li><strong>Production:</strong> Tree-shaking, optimization</li></ul><p class=\"text-block\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #00ffb3; font-weight: bold;\">Design systems made easy! Next: Combine with your favorite JS framework 🚀</p></div><div class=\"page-nav-buttons bottom-nav\"><button class=\"btn-secondary prev-btn\">❮ Previous</button><button class=\"btn-primary next-btn\" disabled>Next ❯</button></div>"}]
